    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔称美联储降息时机已到</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/powell-says-time-has-come-for-fed-to-cut-interest-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔表示，现在是下调关键政策利率的时候了，这肯定了人们对官员们将于下个月开始降低借贷成本的预期，并明确表示他打算防止劳动力市场进一步降温。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/powell-says-time-has-come-for-fed-to-cut-interest-rates</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥比索飙升，鲍威尔暗示降息，引领新兴市场反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/emerging-markets-set-to-cap-weekly-gains-as-traders-await-powell</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席鲍威尔表示调整货币政策的时机已经到来，新兴市场股市和货币随之上涨，带动风险资产上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/emerging-markets-set-to-cap-weekly-gains-as-traders-await-powell</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 10:36:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
